Name: Shrine to Anubis
About the game: Welcome Brave Explorer You have recently discovered a map to the fabled Shrine to Anubis deep in the Kaylo desert. After days of travel you finally find the temple to Anubis's shrine. But who said exploring was going to be easy? Jump, dodge, and loot your way through increasingly hard levels as you try to find Anubis' final resting place. Just so you can prove to all your other college professors that the ancient Egyptian gods were real! Good luck brave adventurer!
